ound\">{activity.time}</p>\n                        </div>\n                        </div>\n                    ))}\n                    </div>\n                </CardContent>\n            </Card>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n  )\n}\n", "type": "registry:block", "target": "src/components/widget-1.tsx"}], "type": "registry:block"}